asset.author: Victorinox AG
asset.hookText:
This year stands out for the 130 years anniversary of our now legendary Swiss army knife but we’re also celebrating the 25th anniversary of the watchmaking brand, Victorinox Swiss Army. For those reasons, Victorinox Swiss Army just announced a partnership with the Fire Department City of New York, the much acclaimed FDNY Foundation, but also with the Swiss fire unit of Ibach in Switzerland, city where Victorinox has its headquarters.
Read more on Victorinoxwatches.com or click here http://goo.gl/nIz1nj
